nvicted-over-plot-to-murder-man-outside-familys-london-restaurant-after-100000-demand/articleshow/131547405.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-06T13:45:24+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131547514,imgsize-567643.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA['Didn't want to be Jimmy Carter': Trump shares why US troops didn't extract Iran's uranium]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131546920.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[President Trump revealed a shelved plan to militarily extract Iran's enriched uranium, deeming it too risky. Despite this, he asserted the US capability to seize the material, which he described as "entombed" and secure.  Meanwhile, US envoys consulted specialists for upcoming nuclear talks with Tehran, though significant divisions persist.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/didnt-want-to-be-jimmy-carter-trump-shares-why-us-troops-didnt-extract-irans-uranium/articleshow/131546920.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/middle-east/didnt-want-to-be-jimmy-carter-trump-shares-why-us-troops-didnt-extract-irans-uranium/articleshow/131546920.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-06T13:23:11+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">TOI World Desk</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131547230,imgsize-68828.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[Fact check: Did Tyla really get N3on kicked out of a Celebrity Dinner in Monaco? What really happened during the livestream]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131542762.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[A viral social media rumor falsely claimed singer Tyla got streamer N3on removed from a celebrity dinner in Monaco after he filmed her during a livestream. The controversy exploded after several X accounts misidentified an Instagram model as the Grammy-winning artist. Posts alleged security threats and a heated confrontation, but fans later pointed out the woman in the video was not Tyla. The incident quickly became another example of how misinformation spreads online when viral clips and celebrity culture collide.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/fact-check-did-tyla-really-get-n3on-kicked-out-of-a-celebrity-dinner-in-monaco-what-really-happened-during-the-livestream/articleshow/131542762.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/fact-check-did-tyla-really-get-n3on-kicked-out-of-a-celebrity-dinner-in-monaco-what-really-happened-during-the-livestream/articleshow/131542762.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-06T05:52:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131542762,imgsize-42302.cms"/></item><item><title><![CDATA[“You and your fake husband....": Candace Owens accuses Laura Loomer of lying about her marriage in explosive social media feud]]></title><description>&lt;img border="0" hspace="10" align="left" style="margin-top:3px;margin-right:5px;" src="https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/photo/131542746.cms" /&gt;<![CDATA[Laura Loomer and Candace Owens ignited a fierce online feud after Loomer accused Owens of using her Russia trip to prepare for possible asylum if investigated for alleged FARA violations. Loomer also speculated about Owens’ pregnancy. Owens fired back with a deeply personal response, accusing Loomer of lying about her relationship and mocking her Alaskan cruise photos. Their explosive exchange quickly went viral, drawing intense reactions across social media and further escalating tensions between the two controversial conservative personalities.]]></description><link><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/you-and-your-fake-husband-candace-owens-accuses-laura-loomer-of-lying-about-her-marriage-in-explosive-social-media-feud/articleshow/131542746.cms]]></link><guid><![CDATA[https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/us-streamers/you-and-your-fake-husband-candace-owens-accuses-laura-loomer-of-lying-about-her-marriage-in-explosive-social-media-feud/articleshow/131542746.cms]]></guid><pubDate>2026-06-06T05:31:00+05:30</pubDate><dc:creator xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/">Barsha Dutta</dc:creator><enclosure type="image/jpeg" url="https://static.toiimg.com/photo/msid-131542746,imgsize-38200.cms"/></item></channel></rss>